# User History API

## Overview
Retrieve a user's game transaction history.

## Endpoints

GET    /api/UserHistory/user/{userId}  
    Get game history for a specific user.  
    - Path parameter: userId (int) â€” User identifier.  
    - Returns: Array of user history records.

## Error Responses

- 401: Unauthorized.
- 404: User or history not found.
- 500: Server error.

